      "text": [
        " صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ: «اَلصَّدَقَةُ بِعَشَرَةٍ وَ اَلْقَرْضُ بِثَمَانِيَةَ عَشَرَ وَ صِلَةُ اَلْإِخْوَانِ بِعِشْرِينَ وَ صِلَةُ اَلرَّحِمِ بِأَرْبَعَةٍ وَ عِشْرِينَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1738 - The Messenger of Allah (swt), peace and blessings be upon him and his family, said:\n\"Charity is rewarded tenfold, a loan eighteenfold, kindness to brothers twentyfold, and maintaining ties of kinship twenty-fourfold.\""
        ]
      }
    },
